tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE assignments (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id UUID,
    assignment_name VARCHAR,
    grade INT,
    feedback TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Grades (
  grade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id INT,
  assignment_id INT,
  score FLOAT,
  feedback VARCHAR,
  FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (assignment_id) REFERENCES Assignments(assignment_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Assignments (
  assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id INT,
  assignment_name TEXT,
  grade DECIMAL,
  feedback TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Grades (
  grade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id INT,
  assignment_id INT,
  grade VARCHAR(10),
  feedback TEXT
);
